@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 190

actor "Nhan vien" as Staff
participant "StaffFeaturePanels.contractPanel\n(View)" as View
participant "StaffFeatureController\n(Facade)" as Facade
participant "ContractController" as Controller
participant "StaffService" as Service
participant "StaffContractRepository" as Repository
participant "JpaStaffDataStore" as DataStore
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over Staff, DB: QUY TRINH LAP HOP DONG VA NHAN PHONG MOI

Staff -> View : 1. Chon phong trong + nhap thong tin khach/hop dong
View -> Facade : 2. createContract(roomCode,...,rent,deposit)
activate Facade

Facade -> Controller : 3. createContract(roomCode,...)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service : 4. addContractFull(roomCode,...)
activate Service
Service -> Repository : 5. addContractFull(roomCode,...)
activate Repository
Repository -> DataStore : 6. addContractFull(roomCode,...)
activate DataStore

DataStore -> DB : 7. Tao tenant + contract + update room DA_THUE
activate DB
DB -->> DataStore : 8. Luu thanh cong
DataStore -->> Repository : 9. ContractItem moi
Repository -->> Service : 10. ContractItem moi
Service -->> Controller : 11. ContractItem moi
Controller -->> Facade : 12. Hoan tat tao hop dong
Facade -->> View : 13. Thong bao tao hop dong thanh cong

deactivate DB
deactivate DataStore
deactivate Repository
deactivate Service
deactivate Controller
deactivate Facade

View -> View : 14. Refresh table contracts() va quay ve Trang chu
View -->> Staff : 15. Hien message box lap hop dong thanh cong
@enduml
